{"tid":1394684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好放棄！有個人同我地一樣喺呢場運動背水一戰緊","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:31:19.000Z","uid":246250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac4f3ea0cd96ffdd904b35da00fd1182e6f6a8c","tid":1394684,"uid":246250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"嗰個人就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">習近平！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好肯定而家佢急過我地，佢一急就亂。由71到而家已經證明咗佢每一步棋都行撚錯曬</span><br />\n<br />\n我地要智取，唔想再有義士被捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">85大罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n知己知彼，想知習種既成長之路，可以睇睇。<br />\n有殘體字，慎入。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abcchinese.au/videos/2064829833553302?s=100003760880899&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabcchinese.au%2Fvideos%2F2064829833553302%3Fs%3D100003760880899%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=6dda17b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abcchinese.au/videos/2064829833553302?s=100003760880899&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n簡述一下條片內容：<br />\n<br />\n1. 習近平喺成長其間經歷文革，老豆被批評，家姐死撚咗。但佢冇憎恨共產黨，反而仲申請入黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。極度懷疑佢當時已經心理變態，毫無親情道德可言<br />\n<br />\n2. 喺佢仲做緊副主席其間，就已經喺外訪期間擺出強硬立場，話外國政府食飽飯無屎屙，咪撚插手中國嘅事，導致新疆、西藏自治區全部冇人去理！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00805d1f6c5a6eef0febda862b89f8dff0c680c8","tid":1394684,"uid":246250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B681Fxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB681Fxb.png&h=9eb8d8a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4beda15c09ec42f06feb0302db17ac4592a770da","tid":1394684,"uid":246250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"